Kasee kalu i kuu ba'apata, alaka' pirurup, kasi minamina'i a wuukmuu.
“Pinsoop na soopan men itiu', gause balaki' a soopan tia salan men mae' na kosilaka'an. Ka' uga' biai' a mian men minsoop lumiu na soopan balaki' iya'a.
