Upa men Yaku' bantilkon na ko'omuu men tongko' kuu-kuuna a nongorongor, tadulkon iya'a na mian biai'. Ka' upa men Yaku' seasoikon na tilingamuu, lelekon na mian biai'.
Kasee giigii' nabii ka' kitap Torat pataka i Yohanes nuntundun upa men tio bo sida.
Gause Anak Manusia a bo Pinginti'i na ilio Sabat.”
Mbali' iya'a, bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' giigii' dosa ka' wurung men mingiroki mian dauga' sida ampunion! Kasee kalu ia mingiroki Alus Molinas, ia sian sida ampunion!
Kasi murit ni Yesus notaka na Ko'ona nobapikirawar taena, “Nongko'upa i Kuu se' batimbaani' kalu batundun na mian biai'?”
Sobii rua-rua'na bi tuo' pataka tempona pamadakan. Bantilkononkusi na mian men mamadak se' tambun kutung a padangna, koot, kasi tunu. Moko daa iya'a, kasi posuu'onku mantambun gandumna ka' manganaa' na alangku.’ ”
Ka' taasi' giigii' utus-Na wiwine dumodongo iraani'i tii kita? Se' daa maana a nantausian-Na giigii' iya'a?”
Kasee liuliu ia simbati i Yesus tae-Na, “Porampot a noamuu! Yaku' ini'i. Alia layaon!”
Kasee upa ba'idek men umuar na nganga' sabole mimpu'u na noa, ka' iya'a a men mengerere wakana mian.
Raaya'a nuntumbeimo pootunduni taena, “Ai Ia nangaan koiya'a gause i kita sian nangawawa roti.”
Tempo i raaya'a notumokuru na buu'na iya'a, Yesus nomotoomo i raaya'a tae-Na, “Alia montoobantilkonkuu ni imepo aupa men kuu piile' umba'a kalu Anak Manusia sianpo potuo'ion moko daa lapus.”
Too matamuu a manggau'kon i kuu baradosa, kuati ka' balo'kon a matamuu inono'! Mbulokon i kuu mampisok sambotak kasee daa tumuo' tia Alaata'ala pookokoikonon tia dauga' isian rua-rua'na matamuu kasee i kuu tibarkonon na apuna naraka.”
Ia simbati i Yesus tae-Na, “Sianpo mbali' i kuu nambasa na Alkitaap se' i Ia men ninsidakon mian tumbena ninsidakon i raaya'a moro'one tia wiwine?
Toro jaammo sembilan ma'ulop, tombono ale' iya'a no'umuarmo soosoodo kasi nimiile' toropii mian men sian palimangonna iraando'o na tampat pobalukan ka' ba'ilianna mian.
Isian rua' mian mampisok poto'oruang na soripi'na salan. Sarataa i raaya'a nongorongor se' i Yesus nolumiu, raaya'a nangkakaro'mo taena, “Tumpu, lee' ni Daud! Kolingu'konon i kai!”
Nimiile' upa men nosida iya'a, samba' a murit ni Yesus. Raaya'a nimikirawarmo taena, “Koi upa se' daa liuliu nalau a kau ara kale'e?”
Mbali' iya'a, bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' Batomundo'anna Alaata'ala bo alaon na ko'omuu ka' bo rookonon na sa'angu' lipu' men daa mingilimang upa men kana' na Batomundo'an iya'a. [
Utusna men korua'na uga' koiya'a ka' men kotolu'na ka' pataka men kopitu'na.
Raaya'a beleskon angga'ionna mian na pasar ka' mingkira' leelo'on Guru.
Yerusalem! Yerusalem! Nabii kuu papatei. Mian men ia posuu' Alaata'ala kuu lapak tia watu pataka lapus! Piribiai'mo i Yaku' mingkira' mongoroot giigii' mian men dumodongo na ko'omuu koi sinana siok mongopo'i anakna na intuna laina, kasee i kuu bude'!
Gause kotakaanna Anak Manusia bo sida koi kilap men tarang dumilep ringkat na bete'an taka na sopokan.
Tanga'na rondom, kasi nirongor a mian mengeleelo'kon taena, ‘Takamo a suo' moro'one! Mai laboti i ia.’
Tempo i Yaku' sian pakeanan, kuu nantarai i Yaku' pakean. Tempo i Yaku' nanggeo, kuu nandagai i Yaku'. Tempo i Yaku' nitarungku, kuu nengelego'i Yaku'.’
Sarataa malommo, Yesus no'umoruangmo kumaan ruru-ruru' tia sompulo' rua' murit-Na.
Mian men mongorookon i Yesus noko pambantilkonmo oosan kani'imari na ko'ona i raaya'a: “Mian men ookionku, ya'amo i Ia. Rakop i Ia.”
Ka' na tempo iya'a nuntuturuu'mo a siok.
Sarataa i Pilatus nunsuri se' ia sian moko ba'upa, ka' mian biai' kaekae' dodoa gora', ia nangalamo weer ka' ningoso' na aropna mian biai' ka' norobu taena, “Yaku' sian sala' na rara'na mian kani'i. Ya'a urusanmuu!”
Tanaasna surudadu tia surudaduna men mandagai i Yesus nolayaonmo tuu'. Sarataa i raaya'a nunsuri lili' ka' upa men nosida, raaya'a norobumo taena, “Mian kani'i tuutuu' Anakna Alaata'ala!”
Yesus nangkarani' i raaya'a ka' norobu tae-Na, “Giigii' kuasa na surugaa tia na tano' balaki' nirookonmo na Ingku'.
“Oo Yesus samba Nazaret, aupa a urusaan tii kai? Kabai i Koo taka bo pinsilaka'i i kai? Inti'ionku se' i ime i Koo: Koo a men Molinas nda'ara'amari na Alaata'ala.”
Aupa a daana, mangaan na mian repo' kani'i, ‘Dosaam daa ni'ampunimo,’ kabai se' mangaan, ‘Wangonmo, leengket a ueraan ka' tumpang?’
Mian men lampingionna meena, kalu mimiile' i Yesus, tonsungol na arop-Na, ka' i raaya'a mangkakaro', taena, “Koomo mba'a a men anak na Alaata'ala.”
Isian uga' men nandawo' na karabatu, men sian laan tano'na. Wine' iya'a liuliu notumuo' gause tano'na monipis.
Kasee tempo i ia nikambur, ia tumuo' ka' uminsur labi gala sambanaan, kasi mimpanga' biai' ka' moola', mau sapu'po sida mimpeeta ka' lilungionna.”
Mian iya'a uga' nomae'mo ka' nuntundunkon mian na libutan Dekapolis upa men ia wawau i Yesus na ko'ona. Wiwi'na mian men nongorongor tundunanna iya'a nosamba'mo.
Noko daa iya'a ai Yesus nomae'mo na kampung men tiku-tikum pookarani' ka' nimisiso' mian.
Sarataa i Yesus nalau na duangan ka' nimiile' mian biai' iya'a, Ia nolingu'mo, gause i raaya'a somo koi domba men sianta mian nontondong. Mbaka' Ia nimisiso'konmo biai' upa na ko'ona i raaya'a.
Koiya'a mba'a mbali' mian Farisi tia wawa ukum Torat nimikirawar ni Yesus, taena, “Nongko'upa a murit-Muu se' sian mongololoikon adatna pulinta? Nongko'upa i raaya'a se' kumaan see sian mingoso'?”
Tongko' indo'o, isian mian nangawawa na Ko'ona sa'angu' mian men umu' ka' mabongol. Raaya'a nama'ase' kada' i Yesus mengepetkon limana na mian iya'a.
Noko daa koiya'a, ai Yesus tia murit-Na notakamo na Betsaida. Na Betsaida isian mian nangawawa sa'angu' mian mampisok ni Yesus, ka' nama'ase' na ko'ona kada' daa koyongon-Na ka' lesi'ion.
Kasee bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' i Elia noko takamo, ka' mian biai' nangawawaukon i Ia koi pingkira'na i raaya'a. Ya'a kana'mo tia men nitulis na Alkitaap men muntundun waka-Na.”
Imamat a men taeng-Ku', ka' uga' bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' mian men mimi'inumi i kuu, montoodaa i kuu lolo' ni Kristus, ia sabole-bole mantausi tambona.”
Yesus nintioki mian iya'a ka' nolingu', kasi i Ia norubu, tae-Na, “Dauga' sangkaliangan a men koo'po koo wawau. Rae' ka' balukkon a giigii' upaam ka' rookon a doi'na bona mian talalais. Kalu koiya'a, koo bo mokosue kupang na surugaa. Moko daa kasi taka mongololo' i Yaku'.”
Mbaka' ia leelo'mo i raaya'a a mian mampisok iya'a. Kasi taena i raaya'a, “Popotaan a noaam! Mai ringkat. Ai koo Ia leelo' i Yesus.”
Ia simbati i Yesus tae-Na, “Parasayamo na Alaata'ala.
Kasee i Yesus inti-inti'i panduungna i raaya'a, kasi tae-Na, “Nongko'upa i kuu se' mimitopongi i Yaku'? Wawa le'emari a sa'angu' doi' dinar kada' piile'on-Ku.”
Raaya'a mo'uus umoruang na oruangan men porena na laigan bakitumpuan kabai na pootatakaianna mian biai'.
Bitu'on bo mandawo' ra'amari na langit ka' pungkuasai langit iya'a bo toyunggot.
Poto'oruang i raaya'a kumaan, ai Yesus norobumo tae-Na, “Imamat ini'imari! Bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' isian i kuu men bo mongorookon i Yaku' kada' papateion, men pintanga' kumaan tii Yaku'.”
Yesus norobu na ko'ona i raaya'a tae-Na, “Pansaruimuu se' i Yaku' too mian puraga mbali' i kuu taka poto'inton bakoko' tia popool bo pangarakop i Yaku'?
Kasee i Yesus santaa'po sianmo ninsimbati, tamban i Pilatus nosamba'mo.
Nomorongor iya'a, toropii mian men potokerer iraando'o norobu taena, “Rongor, Ia mengeleelo' i Elia.”
ka' mau mingintoni ule, kabai se' minginum rasung, raaya'a sian nongko'upa. Ka' mian manggeo, kalu epetonna i raaya'a tia limana, sida malesi'.”
Malaa'ikat iya'a notakamo ni Maria ka' norobu taena, “Tabea' na ko'oom, wiwine men nibarakaati! Tumpu mandagai i koo.”
ka' Ia momosuu' mian kupangon mae' tia lima sompulo'.
kasee i kita sidamo monsoosa' i Ia tia noa men maloos ka' molinas tempo i kita dauga' tumuo' na tano' balaki'.
Pontotobo' domba iya'a nomule'konmo na dodongoanna. Ka' banta-bantang mule'kon, raaya'a muntunde' ka' mompopobalaki' Alaata'ala gause giigii' men ia piile' ka' ia rongor i raaya'a, sintuutuu' tia upa men ia bantilkon malaa'ikat na ko'ona i raaya'a.
Minti'i-Napo samba' nimiile' i Ia. Mbaka' sina-Na norobumo na Ko'ona taena, “Anakku, nongko'upa i Koo se' mangawawau koi kani'i na ko'omai? Tamaam tii yaku' noleapkonmo i Koo!”
Kasee ka' i Yohanes nambantili i Herodes, men tomundo' na libutan Galilea, gause i Herodes nosuo' tii Herodias boroki'na utusna, ka' uga' gause giigii' idek men ia wawaumo,
Kosam anak ni Elmadam,
Ishak anak ni Abraham,
Noko daa iya'a, Ibiliis nangawawamo i Yesus na Yerusalem ka' nongowoot i Ia na wuunganna Laiganna Alaata'ala, kasi norobu ni Yesus taena, “Kalu se' i Koo Anakna Alaata'ala, alaka' tumbur waaro'o!
Kasee i Yesus nengerengeaki meena iya'a tae-Na, “Pimporokot! Uarmo i koo na mian kanono'!” Mbaka' meena iya'a ningirimpa'konmo mian iya'a na tanga'na mian biai', kasi no'umuar namarerei mian iya'a, kasee daa sian nampapolosi i ia.
Sarataa i Yesus nimiile' wawauna i raaya'a se' parasaya tuu' na Ko'ona, Ia norobumo na mian iya'a tae-Na, “Utus! Dosaam daa ni'ampunimo.”
Kasee wawa ukum Torat tia toropii mian Farisi iya'a noburuki'mo tuu', ka' i raaya'a nopootunduniimo se' too upaionmo i Yesus.
Upa men kikira'muu wawauonna mian na ko'omuu, wawau uga' a men koiya'a na ko'ona i raaya'a.
Tempo i Yesus torumpakmo na soopanna kota, isian mian biai' nunguer biibii mae' na baleanan. Mian men nolapus iya'a anak moro'one suusuungna, ia anakna sa'angu' wiwine men nobalumo. Biai' a mianna kota nomae' tia balu iya'a.
Isian sa'angu' mian Farisi nangange i Yesus kada' kumaan na laiganna. Yesus nomae'mo na laiganna mian Farisi iya'a ka' nokumaan.
Wine' men nandawo' na karabatu mase mian men na tempo nongorongor wurung iya'a, ia nangalabotmo tia noa beles. Kasee wurung iya'a sian niwakat na noana i raaya'a. Raaya'a parasaya kasee tongko' kodi-kodi', ka' tempo takaionna solon-solong, raaya'a minsasapu kaparasaya'anna.
“Ule'konmo na laigaan ka' lelekon a giigii' upa men ia wawaumo Alaata'ala na ko'oom.”
Poposuu' ni Yesus nomule'konmo ka' nuntundunkon ni Yesus giigii' men ia wawau i raaya'a. Yesus nangangemo i raaya'a ka' mae' nintisaal na kota Betsaida.
Koi liilana i Yesus tia murit-Na totolu' notumokurumo na buu'na iya'a, ka' mian biai' notakamo na Ko'ona.
Rae'mo! Imamat ini'imari! Yaku' momosuu' i kuu koi anakna domba na tanga'na serigala.
Kasee komburi'na isian samba Samaria men na rae'anna uga' nolumiu indo'o. Sarataa ia nimiile' mian iya'a, notongkibitmo a noana gause nolingu'.
Kasee i Yesus ninginti'i noana mian iya'a. Mbaka' i Ia norobumo na ko'ona i raaya'a tae-Na, “Kalu sa'angu' batomundo'an pookakaresa ka' sian pooka'amat, batomundo'an iya'a sabole sianmo umimput. Kalu sa'angu' suo' pookakaresa ka' sian pooka'amat, suo' iya'a sabole sian bakitaan.
Ia simbati i Yesus tae-Na, “Silaka' i kuu wawa ukum Torat! Kuu momosuu' mian mingilimang men marawat, kasee i kuu toro tiu'po sian muntulung mian kada' sida mingilimang men koiya'a.
Kasi i Yesus norobu na murit-Na tae-Na, “Mbali' iya'a, bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu se' alia i kuu babatakon tutuo'muu, na upa men bo kaanon ka' inumonmuu. Alia babatakon wakamuu na upa men bo pakeanmuu.
Muntumbei koini'i, suo' men isian lima' mian sianmo pokakana'. Totolu' mintimbangi rurua' kabai rurua' mintimbangi totolu'.
Kasi isian mian men nimikirawar na Ko'ona taena, “Tumpu, tongko' titiu' a mian men daa bo salamatkonon?”
Kasee i Yesus norobu na mian iya'a tae-Na, “Isian sa'angu' mian nangawawau ramean men balaki' ka' nengeleelo' mian biai'.
Yesus norobu soosoodo tae-Na, “Isian sa'angu' mian men anakon moro'one rurua'.
Noko daa koiya'a ia norobumo na mian korua'na taena, ‘Pipii a samayaam?’
Kalu utusmuu sa'angu' kaparasaya'an baradosa, bantili i ia. Kalu ia minsosol, ampuni i ia.
Inau' a upa men nosida na boroki' ni Loot!
Yesus ninginti'i se' mian iya'a masiongo' tuu' a noana. Mbali' iya'a, Ia norobumo tae-Na, “Marepa tuu' a mian kupangon minsida mianna Batomundo'anna Alaata'ala!
Gause Anak Manusia taka bo mansarak ka' mansalamatkon mian men sian mamarasaya Alaata'ala.”
Bi pore na surugaa!
Yesus nintiokimo i raaya'a kasi nangaan tae-Na, “Kalu koiya'a, upa aratina isiina Alkitaap men koi kani'imari:
Alaka' oruang na paraas uanan-Ku,
“Bo isian oosan na matana ilio, wulan ka' bitu'on. Giigii' lipu' na tano' balaki' bo babata ka' layaon mongorongor kokuungna bokol ka' mimiile' tobui men makansang.
Noko daa koiya'a i Yesus nanganakatmo sasangkir men isian anggur, nobasukuur na Alaata'ala, kasi norobu tae-Na, “Ala kani'i, ka' poo'obos.
Noko daa nosambayang, Yesus nomule'konmo soosoodo na murit-Na. Ia takai i Yesus i raaya'a nokoroyotmo gause masiongo'.
Kasi i raaya'a norobu taena, “Bo upa ka' dauga' mansarak mian bo pinginti'ianta! Daa kita rongormo a men Ia porobukon!”
Imamat ini'imari! Bo taka tempona mian bo mangaan, ‘Barakaatan a wiwine men sian nontoo pampaiwawa, men sian nontoo anakon ka' sian nontoo pomosusui anak ngamea'!’
Na iliona Minggu, ma'ulo-ulop tuu' toropii wiwine iya'a nomae'mo na baleanan nangawawa rampa men ia toropotimo i raaya'a.
Kasee i raaya'a nantaankonmo i Ia. Taena, “Tuuk kutung na ko'omai. Koini'i boomo malom ka' uga' muntumbeimo pika'.” Mbaka' i Yesus notuukmo tii raaya'a.
Isian sa'angu' mian men notaka ia posuu' Alaata'ala. Ngaanna i Yohanes.
Tempo i yaku' sianpo nimiile' Alus Molinas nda'amari langit, yaku' sianpo ninginti'i i Ia. Kasee Alaata'ala men nomosuu' i yaku' mansarani tia weer nambantilkon na ingku' tae-Na, ‘Kalu i koo mimiile' Alus Molinas malau na sa'angu' mian, mbaka' mian men palauionna nono'mo a men bo mansarani tia Alus Molinas.’
Kasi i Yesus norobu na ko'ona tae-Na, “Alaka' tauk a weer kanono' titiu' ka' wawakon na tanaasna ramean.” Mbaka' ia wawakonmo i raaya'a a weer iya'a na tanaasna ramean,
Sianta sa'angu'po a mian men nomae' na surugaa saliwakon Anak Manusia men nalau nda'amari na surugaa.
Sian nanau' notakamo a sa'angu' wiwine samba Samaria mae' tumambu'. Yesus norobumo na wiwine iya'a tae-Na, “Sida i Yaku' mama'ase' minginum?”
Mian men mamadak noko pangalabotmo tambona, ka' nantambun ule' bona tutuo'na men pore pataka sidutu. Mbaka' mian men nangasok ka' mian men namadak koikoimo munsuri beles.
Mbali' iya'a moomoola'na Yahudi norobumo na mian men baasi nalesi' iya'a taena, “Koini'i ilio Sabat. Koo sian sida mamasa'an ampaas.”
kasee i kuu bude' taka na Ingku' kada' mantausi tutuo' men pore pataka sidutu iya'a.
Tempo iya'a isian toro pii duangan men ringkat na kota Tiberias notaka ka' nobalabu karani' tampat men nangkaananna mian biai' roti noko daa ia sukuurkon i Tumpu Yesus.
Kasi taeni Yesus, “Imamat a men taeng-Ku', ka' uga' bantilkonon-Ku na ko'omuu kalu i kuu sian mangkaan antokna Anak Manusia ka' minginum rara'-Na, kuu sian mantausi tutuo' men pore pataka sidutu.
Ka' biai' a mian pooseasoi muntundun i Ia. Isian mian men mangaan: “Ia mian ma'amat.” Isian uga' men mangaan: “Sian, Ia mantarai pisiso' sala' na mian biai'.”
Kasee men sambana uga' norobu taena, “Taasi'. Tomundo' Pansalamatkon taasi' ringkat na Galilea!
Kasee kalu i Yaku' mungukumi, mbaka' pungukuming-Ku iya'a tuutuu', gause i Yaku' taasi' tongko' suung-Ku, kasee Yaku' poopoololo' tii Ia men nomosuu' i Yaku'.
Taeni Yesus, “Kalu se' Alaata'ala iya'a Tamamuu, kuu bo molingu'kon i Yaku', gause i Yaku' ringkat na Alaata'ala. Ka' i Yaku' taka taasi' tongko' pingkira'-Ku, kasee pingkira'-Na men nomosuu' i Yaku'.
Taena i raaya'a, “Aanamo a mian iya'a?”
Taeni Yesus, “Yaku' taka na tano' balaki' bo pungukumi, kada' ime a men sian poopiile' sidakonon poopiile', ka' ime a men mangaan se' wakana daa poopiile', ia bo sidakonon mampisok.”
Yaku' mantarai i raaya'a tutuo' men pore pataka sidutu ka' i raaya'a sianta lapus. Sianta sa'angu'po mian men momoko mangarampasi i raaya'a na limang-Ku.
Tomas men ngaanon i Rapi' norobu na murit ni Yesus sambana taena, “Mai kita lumolo', sobii mau i kita pate tii ia!”
Mbaka' no'umuarmo a mian men nolapusmo iya'a. Limana tia saratna dauga'na balu-balun tia toik pobalun biibii, ka' ro'upna dauga'na sa'u-sa'ubi tia toik sasa'ubi ro'up. Kasi i Yesus norobu na mian men iraando'o tae-Na, “Anui a toik pobalunna kada' i ia sida mae'!”
Yesus nantausi sa'angu' keledai rundara bo nolakitan-Na. Mbaka' nosidamo a men nitulis na Alkitaap taena,
Raaya'a sian parasaya, gause i Yesaya uga' isian nangaan taena,
Yaku' mantarai pisiso' kani'i na ko'omuu, kada' i kuu uga' mangawawau upa men Yaku' poko wawaumo na ko'omuu.
Ia simbati i Yesus tae-Na, “Yaku'mo a salan, ka' Yaku' a men kana', ka' Yaku' a bo pantarai tutuo' men pore pataka sidutu. Sianta sa'angu'po mian a men taka na Tama na surugaa kalu sianta tii Yaku'.
Kuu tio poowawa pore tii Yaku' kada' i Yaku' uga' poowawa pore tii kuu. Koimo panga' sian sida miwoo' suungna kalu sian motokantang tia pu'una, koiya'a uga' i kuu sian sida miwoo' kalu i kuu sian poowawa pore tii Yaku'.
Ka' koini'i noamuu nasiongo'mo gause i Yaku' nambantilkon men koiya'a na ko'omuu.
Kalu mian minginti'i i Kuu, Alaata'ala men sa'a-sa'angu' ka' men kana', ka' uga' minginti'i i Yesus Kristus men Kuu posuu', mbaka' koiya'a a salan kada' daa mantausi tutuo' men pore pataka sidutu.
Yudas men ba'idek a noana ni Yesus uga' indo'o potokerer tii raaya'a.
Kasee taena samba Yahudi, “Kai sian sida mungukum mian tia ukuman pate.”
Ia simbati tanaasna imam taena, “Tomundo'mai tongko' Kaisar, sianta sambanaan!”
Raaya'a rua' ira nangalamo biibii ni Yesus ka' nambalun tia toik pobalun ka' nintimbu'i tia minamina' iya'a mongololo' koi adatna samba Yahudi kalu mantanom biibii.
Mbaka' murit ni Yesus men sambana norobumo ni Tomas taena, “Kai nimiile'mo Tumpu!”
Koporotoluna i Yesus nimikirawar na ko'ona tae-Na, “Simon, anak ni Yohanes, tuutuu' i koo mongkolingu'kon i Yaku'?”
Taeni Petrus, “Na kitap Mazmur isian nitulis koi kani'imari,
ka' minti'imuu bo mingipi men Yaku' popo'ipikon na ko'ona i raaya'a.
Mbali' iya'a giigii' samba Israel tio tuutuu' minginti'i se' Alaata'ala nangawawaumo i Yesus men kuu saliip iya'a nosidamo Tumpu ka' Tomundo' Pansalamatkon.”
Utu-utus! Mbali' iya'a, sosoli ka' kadaraimo a wawaumuu men ba'idek, ka' parasaya a Alaata'ala kada' sapuion-Na wiwi'na dosamuu,
Mian men nilesi'i tia wawau kosamba' iya'a labimo patompulo' taun a umurna.
